    "Name": "Yun Qi RR-S7Y",
    "Details": "The Yun Qi RR-S7Y is a 50-ton mixed-technology arena BattleMech built by Firefly Foundry in 3105 using Clan Sea Fox hardware acquired through the Rangers' partnership with the Clan. A left-torso Clan Gauss Rifle delivers precise heavy fire at range, backed by two right-torso ER Medium Lasers. A right-arm Chain Whip provides melee disruption capability, while a left-torso Streak SRM 2 and four left-arm ER Micro Lasers handle confirmed close-range damage. Endo Steel structure and Ferro-Fibrous armor maximize protection within the medium weight class.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Variable Range Targeting</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.04</color></b>",
